      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Infra_RedisCache作为初始状态，然后流转到IsPositive判断节点。这个IsPositive是一个状态还是判断条件？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "IsPositive"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "IsPositive是一个状态节点，表示正在判断数值。真正做分支判断的是后面的choice节点，需要根据数值结果分成两条路径：False和True。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IsPositive",
        "choice",
        "False",
        "True"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，我理解了。结构是：Infra_RedisCache → IsPositive → choice节点，然后choice分出False和True两个分支。这个choice节点我命名为if_state可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "IsPositive",
        "if_state",
        "False",
        "True"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，if_state这个名字很贴切。注意False分支的条件是n < 0，True分支的条件是n = 0。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "if_state",
        "False",
        "True"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把结构画出来了。Infra_RedisCache指向IsPositive，IsPositive指向if_state这个choice节点，然后if_state分别指向False和True，并标注了对应的条件。您看一下是否符合预期？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "IsPositive",
        "if_state",
        "False",
        "True"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，条件标注好像反了。False对应的是n < 0，True对应的是n = 0，这个是对的。但我再确认一下——当n=0时走True分支，n<0时走False分支，这样标注没问题。不过我之前说的可能让你误解了，再检查一遍：if_state到False的箭头标注\"if n < 0\"，到True的标注\"if n = 0\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "if_state",
        "False",
        "True"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认无误，if_state → False标注的是\"if n < 0\"，if_state → True标注的是\"if n = 0\"。整个流程：Redis缓存状态进入数值判断，经过choice节点后，负数走False分支，零值走True分支。",
